{
  "description": "A low-angle shot showcases a massive bridge structure against a bright blue sky. The primary focus is on a towering, vertical support beam constructed of steel and concrete. Intricate geometric patterns of metal bracing and beams create a complex network within the structure. Cables extend diagonally from the top of the beam, presumably supporting the bridge deck, which is partially visible below. The lighting is bright and highlights the texture of the materials, with a sense of scale emphasizing the immensity of the construction. There's a hint of atmospheric haze near the top of the structure.",
